Individual




Gerald J. Essl



Mr. Gerald J. Essl is Executive VP-Cement, Aggregates & Concrete at Eagle Materials, Inc.
Mr. Essl was previously employed as President by Texas Lehigh Cement Co. LP and a Principal by United States Marine Corps.
He received his undergraduate degree from Illinois State University.



