Gerald J. Essl's Biography




			Executive Vice President - Cement  (has held current office since April 2016; Executive Vice President - Cement/Aggregates and Concrete from January 2003 through March 2016; President of Texas Lehigh Cement Company from 1985 through December 2002).
		
